Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:28.27,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}It's been so long since we left our home behind
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:34.52,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Drifting on the Milky Way almost every single day
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:37.98,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Where am I supposed to go ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:41.07,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}What're we really looking for ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.41,0:19:46.16,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Stumbling in the darkness, cold and lost
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:53.04,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}But a ray of hope still exists in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:58.55,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Rain or shine, always chase the dream
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:02.68,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Someday, we'll fly across the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.88,0:20:06.14,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Never fearing anything
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.30,0:20:10.93,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}We'll promise that"we'll go on ! "
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:15.11,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Even if you're against the wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:16.61,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Never stop !
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:18.36,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Don't look back !
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:23.78,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}We'll one day rise above it all (never give up)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:27.62,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Who cares if the going's tough
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:29.16,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Never think !
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:31.04,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Keep pushing on !
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:38.13,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}We can find our promised land
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:28.27,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}離鄉遠行 已經歷漫長時光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:34.52,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}年年日日 漂泊在星河八荒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:37.98,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我欲去往何處
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:41.07,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我在追尋何物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.41,0:19:46.16,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}寒冷 迷茫 在黑暗中流浪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:53.04,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}但我心中仍存一線希望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:58.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}無論風雨 始終追尋夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:02.68,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}總有一天 我們將橫越蒼茫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.88,0:20:06.14,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}無所畏懼 展翼翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.30,0:20:10.93,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我們許下誓言 絕不退讓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:15.11,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}即便逆流而上
